  "detailed_description": "<h1>One more cool story!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/31815d5df9ed6154b345e25749bdce14.poster.avif?t=1725747853\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/31815d5df9ed6154b345e25749bdce14.webm?t=1725747853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>✨ A linear visual novel in the adventure and psychological horror genre that tells five short mystical stories that are unrelated at first glance.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/58d7cd0ecd2c1bd6e8d7f8b9782ef894.poster.avif?t=1725747853\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/58d7cd0ecd2c1bd6e8d7f8b9782ef894.webm?t=1725747853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/58d7cd0ecd2c1bd6e8d7f8b9782ef894.mp4?t=1725747853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>👁️ <strong>Mirror</strong><br>When it seems like your day has been the worst of your life, it could always be worse. And sometimes you need to look in the mirror to realize the true cause of your anxiety.<br><br>💳 <strong>Credit card</strong><br>Have you ever wondered how much money you need? And what you would spend it on? One day, a strange card falls into the hands of the heroes of the story at a bus stop...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/e6456e2f88fd418b2956bf6b941693d4.poster.avif?t=1725747853\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/e6456e2f88fd418b2956bf6b941693d4.webm?t=1725747853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/e6456e2f88fd418b2956bf6b941693d4.mp4?t=1725747853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>💾 <strong>Game development</strong><br>Every creative path is thorny. And when you give yourself all to your work, put your soul, you can stay without it.<br><br>👫 <strong>Best Friend</strong><br>The more advances in technology we meet, the more we become distant from people. Then any communication is more valuable than ever, and every friend is worth their weight in gold.<br><br>👽 <strong>Experimentation</strong><br>In a secret laboratory in Sunlight City, an alien creature is being studied, unknown how it came to earth. Since then, mysterious phenomena and strange objects have begun to occur.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/40455a103feaceaaadd1896f7c3ffef7.avif?t=1725747853\" width=592 height=240 /></span><br><br>🍕 A full playthrough will take you 60-90 minutes to complete. Add the game to your wish list, and in the meantime, have some pizza!<br>🎨 The artwork used in this game is created with AI, keep that in mind.<br><br>💡 Join the game's official Discord community to ask any questions, report bugs, ask for keys or just chat! We will be glad to answer any of your requests.<br><br>",
