.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/e6456e2f88fd418b2956bf6b941693d4.webm?t=1725747853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/e6456e2f88fd418b2956bf6b941693d4.mp4?t=1725747853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>💾 <strong>Game development</strong><br>Every creative path is thorny. And when you give yourself all to your work, put your soul, you can stay without it.<br><br>👫 <strong>Best Friend</strong><br>The more advances in technology we meet, the more we become distant from people. Then any communication is more valuable than ever, and every friend is worth their weight in gold.<br><br>👽 <strong>Experimentation</strong><br>In a secret laboratory in Sunlight City, an alien creature is being studied, unknown how it came to earth. Since then, mysterious phenomena and strange objects have begun to occur.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517870/extras/40455a103feaceaaadd1896f7c3ffef7.avif?t=1725747853\" width=592 height=240 /></span><br><br>🍕 A full playthrough will take you 60-90 minutes to complete. Add the game to your wish list, and in the meantime, have some pizza!<br>🎨 The artwork used in this game is created with AI, keep that in mind.<br><br>💡 Join the game's official Discord community to ask any questions, report bugs, ask for keys or just chat! We will be glad to answer any of your requests.<br><br>",
